59
00:04:15,568 --> 00:04:17,596
I forgot my password.

60
00:04:17,596 --> 00:04:19,279
No.

61
00:04:19,279 --> 00:04:24,280
You have to have an account,
so you can follow me when I'm famous.

62
00:04:24,280 --> 00:04:26,320
I'll follow you when you're famous.

63
00:04:26,320 --> 00:04:28,094
No, you have to follow me now.

64
00:04:28,094 --> 00:04:31,520
Give me your phone.
I'll set up a new password for you.

65
00:04:31,520 --> 00:04:33,625
