72
00:05:00,000 --> 00:05:03,828
You're definitely going to remember
your password. It's very easy.

73
00:05:05,142 --> 00:05:06,161
What's the password?

74
00:05:06,161 --> 00:05:07,724
Do you have a paper to note it down?

75
00:05:08,564 --> 00:05:10,923
I have some over there. Go get it yourself.

76
00:05:10,923 --> 00:05:11,987
Okay.

77
00:05:22,189 --> 00:05:23,520
Here.

78
00:05:23,520 --> 00:05:24,472
Moo!

79
00:05:24,472 --> 00:05:26,003
